e 2 below).","Breton (mainly Finistère): from a Frenchified form of the personal name <i>Paol</i>, Breton form of   Paul  .","Irish: shortened Anglicized form of Gaelic <b>Mac Phóil</b> ‘son of Paul’. Compare   McFall  ."]}]},{"name":"Gervais","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Origin uncertain.  See  <b>Gervaise</b> ."],"variants":[]},{"name":"De","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Gervais De Pagnel was born about 1231, in Sulham, Berkshire, England, United Kingdom as the son of Mr Gervase Paganell."},"et":{"ABT 1231–":"umbes 1231–Surnud","1231–Male":"1231–Surnud","1235–Female":"1235–Surnud","1255–1308":"1255–1308","1200–Male":"1200–Surnud","ABT 1231":"umbes 1231","1235":"1235","1255":"1255","1200":"1200","1231":"1231","1308":"1308","Sulham, Berkshire, England":"Sulham, Berkshire, England"},"fi":{"ABT 1231–":"noin 1231–Kuollut","1231–Male":"1231–Kuollut","1235–Female":"1235–Kuollut","1255–1308":"1255–1308","1200–Male":"1200–Kuollut","ABT 1231":"noin 1231","1235":"1235","1255":"1255","1200":"1200","1231":"1231","1308":"1308","Sulham, Berkshire, England":"Sulham, Berkshire, England"},"fr":{"ABT 1231–":"environ 1231–Décédé","1231–Male":"1231–Décédé","1235–Female":"1235–Décédée","1255–1308":"1255–1308","1200–Male":"1200–Décédé","ABT 1231":"environ 1231","1235":"1235","1255":"1255","1200":"1200","1231":"1231","1308":"1308","Sulham, Berkshire, England":"Sulham, Berkshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Gervais De Pagnel est né environ 1231, à Sulham, Berkshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Mr Gervase Paganell."},"de":{"ABT 1231–":"um 1231–Verstorben","1231–Male":"1231–Verstorben","1235–Female":"1235–Verstorben","1255–1308":"1255–1308","1200–Male":"1200–Verstorben","ABT 1231":"um 1231","1235":"1235","1255":"1255","1200":"1200","1231":"1231","1308":"1308",